?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7fzWt7.png&h=b282a0ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36ec620d61c2dc0e54ef2ea0248e4adf7c762c31","tid":1830963,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bL3YDJ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbL3YDJ7.png&h=5106ac60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b51be20e144a1304e2460be6644222d5840d2892","tid":1830963,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"黑警打得，食環狗就同佢客氣？<br />\n咪撚玩喇，見一個打一個"},{"pid":"c207254d9c3bdef2af8105e30529b6d32f64a57c","tid":1830963,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a171a403a74794f59afaa54e7e08a00a86fee2aa","tid":1830963,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"點解無關，人地賣野點宣傳你點知有冇關<br />\n買同賣個個先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:53:55.000Z","msg":"你啱，香港發展商賣樓，D廣告都係洋人在享受生活<br />\n同香港人買件豆腐潤都無關啦"},{"pid":"63d533bee8e77680d77a8c604143acf49c93a43f","tid":1830963,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"場內唔比擺,咪去場外擺<br />\n一日拎一張相企係度"},{"pid":"704cb47683d12c640e9e4b7db5393052624f2b5d","tid":1830963,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98a785373d6f33259ba2be3f20512395fab6e025","tid":1830963,"uid":189430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"704cb47683d12c640e9e4b7db5393052624f2b5d","tid":1830963,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63d533bee8e77680d77a8c604143acf49c93a43f","tid":1830963,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"場內唔比擺,咪去場外擺<br />\n一日拎一張相企係度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:04:08.000Z","msg":